{"type": "article", "id": 2910, "title": "Odd Future 2014秋季帽子系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-17T08:04:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232357BjZh67F1NbsLJrWp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<p>\r\n\t\t美国街头服饰与音乐品牌 Odd Future 最近正式推出了他们为今年秋季设计的帽子系列，设计上主要是以品牌标志性的元素为主，并在传统 Snapback 帽款、冷帽和渔夫帽的基础上，通过“ EARL ”字样，Earl Sweatshirt 卡通头像设计，海豚图案，以及经典的甜甜圈等标志性图案进行点缀，为今年秋季的街头造型增加了几分趣味。定价 32 美元，<a href=\"http://store.hypebeast.com/brands/odd-future/navy-dolphin-donut-cap\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232355Zuk7s2Lbo1pQdqET.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232355ibtSf8zJRHQcYxXo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232356ZX0FhptLmdQ1vCr3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232356kzOZdLSrIgh8CAE1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t<br>\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<div>\r\n\t\t<br>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}